# Project Overview

FivcAdvisor: pattern-driven flows and tools atop CrewAI for building intelligent, multi-agent task flows. Primary entrypoint: Typer CLI `fivcadvisor`. Code under `src/fivcadvisor` (src layout).

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.10+
- Packaging: setuptools via `pyproject.toml`
- CLI: Typer + Rich
- Orchestration: CrewAI `Flow`, `Agent`, `Task`, `Crew`
- LLM config via env (see `src/fivcadvisor/llms.py`)
- Dev tooling: uv, Ruff, Pytest, Makefile

## Repo Layout
- `src/fivcadvisor/` core library
  - `flows/` orchestrators (see `default.py`)
  - `agents.py`, `tasks.py`, `llms.py`, `tools/`, `utils/`
- `tests/` pytest
- `configs/` examples
- `examples/` runnable demos
- `Makefile` common dev commands

## How to run
- Install: `make install` (dev + extras) or `make install-min`
- CLI: `fivcadvisor --help`
- Sample dry-run: `make sample`
